  "description": {
    "zh": "希望你喜欢 AK 系列步枪，在塔科夫你会用它们用到吐。学会怎么改装它们很重要。\n\n我需要你带两把带折叠托的 AKM，一把普通的 AKMS，一把带燕尾座的 AKMSN。规格我都写好了，看你能不能搞定。\n\nAKMS 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 340\n - 重量小于 4.5 公斤\n - 人机功效 44 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 80 %\n - 弹匣容量 20 或更多\n - “射击场”距离 800米 或更多\n - 任意 战术设备\n - AKMS FAB Defense M4-AKMS P Stock Adapter\n\nAKMSN 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 360\n - 重量小于 5.3 公斤\n - 人机功效 34 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 80 %\n - 弹匣容量 40 或更多\n - 任意 消音器\n - 任意 独立战术手电筒\n - OKP-7反射式瞄具 （Dovetail）",
    "en": "I hope you like AK rifles, you'll need to work with them a lot in Tarkov, but I'm just stating the obvious. It would be wise to know how to modify them.\n\nBring me to AKMs with folding stocks, one with and one without a dovetail mount, I'll skip the talking, I wrote down all the specifications for you. Can you manage that?\n\nAKMS Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 340\n - Weight less than 4.5 KG\n - Ergonomics 44 or higher\n - Durability higher than 80 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 20 or more\n - Sighting Range of 800 Meters or more\n - A Tactical Device\n - AKMS FAB Defense M4-AKMS P Stock Adapter\n\nAKMSN Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 360\n - Weight less than 5.3 KG\n - Ergonomics 34 or higher\n - Durability higher than 80 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 40 or more\n - A Silencer\n - A Standalone Flashlight\n - OKP-7 Reflex Sight ( Dovetail )"
  },
